<item>
            <title>[LU-18640] add option for &apos;lfs project&apos; to do project name and id lookup only</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18640</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add options to &apos;&lt;tt&gt;lfs project&lt;/tt&gt;&apos; to lookup the file/directory project id and name in &lt;tt&gt;/etc/projid&lt;/tt&gt; only, without performing any filesystem action.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is useful for test scripts to confirm that &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lfs project&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; itself is looking up the projid/projname correctly in the &lt;tt&gt;/etc/projid&lt;/tt&gt; file, as well as end-user scripts for provisioning, etc.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
